You need to update the configuration files for package repositories. Within which directoryare details of the current package repositories stored on a Debian system?
A)  /etc/apt.list
B)  /etc/sources.list
C)  /etc/apt/sources.list.d/
D)  /etc/apt.d/sources.list
C
C. The /etc/apt/sources.list.d/ directory contains repositories for Debian pack-ages. The other file and directory locations do not exist by default.
